lyrics:
[Intro]
(Soft piano or acoustic guitar melody)


[female voice]
[Verse 1]
Through the labyrinth of time, we journey on
In search of purpose, until the dawn
Life's symphony plays, both gentle and loud
Yet in the shadows, our resolve is found

[Chorus]
In the shadows of the night, we're dancing in the moonlight (ooh-yeah)
In the darkness, we find our strength and ignite (ignite)
Though the world might try to bring us down, we'll rise above the strife (rise above)
In the shadows of the night, we'll keep the fire alive
